---
// The landing is a self-contained, machine-bundled HTML document (all assets
// inlined). We import it verbatim and emit it untouched so Astro never parses
// its markup/scripts. Server-rendered (no prerender) so the Worker answers
// /aiinfinance directly instead of the static-asset layer, whose forced
// trailing-slash redirect loops against Webflow's edge.
import raw from "../index.html?raw";
---
<Fragment set:html={raw} />
